(### 4.1 Assessment Creation) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The Assessment Workspace is the main entry point.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(What the user does:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Select a preferred language.) Tj
T*
(2. Enter profile details such as name, age, village, assessor, and consent.) Tj
T*
(3. Answer the questionnaire items.) Tj
T*
(4. Add a written narrative.) Tj
T*
(5. Optionally provide audio, face image, or passive biomarker inputs.) Tj
T*
(6. View the live preview.) Tj
T*
(7. Save the assessment.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(What the system does:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- validates required fields,) Tj
T*
(- scores the questionnaire,) Tj
T*
(- extracts or estimates text signals,) Tj
T*
(- computes modality confidence and quality,) Tj
T*
(- merges the signals into a multimodal result,) Tj
T*
(- generates recommendation text and disclaimer,) Tj
T*
(- saves the record,) Tj
T*
(- updates analytics and records panels.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### 4.2 Live Preview) Tj
T*
() Tj
